text: The 1965 Soviet Class A Second Group was the third season of the Soviet Class A Second Group football competitions that was established in 1963. It was also the 25th season of the Soviet second tier league competition. ==First stage== ===First Subgroup=== ===Second Subgroup=== ==Final stage== ===For places 1-16=== ====Match for 1st place==== [Nov 25, Grozny] * Ararat Yerevan 2-1 Kayrat Alma-Ata ===For places 17-32=== ==See also== * Soviet First League ==External links== * 1965 season.
